excerpt.rendered:
The Honest Kitchen believes health starts with human-grade, whole foods. We made these one-of-a-kind snacks for picky and sensitive pups by sandwiching cod, fruit, and veggies between layers of crispy cod skin. Packed with omegas and delivered with a satisfying crunch, these bites are so tasty that don’t be surprised if your pup’s fishing for more!
